                        <p>Administrative costs and loads are rising. Institutions must acquire, process and store more
                            data than ever before, and solve the associated infrastructure and data security questions.
                            At the same time, stakeholders increasingly demand ease of use, integration and
                            accessibility. Education entities must reconcile these requirements:</p>
