                        <div class="tile tile-collapse">
                            <h3>Staff & student identity</h3>
                            <div class="text">Verification of staff and student identity is fragmented, with manual
                                record-checking and management costing hours of administrative work.</div>
                            <div class="fade-out"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="tile tile-collapse">
                            <h3>Infrastructure control</h3>
                            <div class="text">IoT allows entities to better manage their electricity, water and
                                appliances, and to track and alert students. But fragmented campus utilities do not
                                offer transparency, rapid data access, or fraud cover.</div>
                            <div class="fade-out"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="tile tile-collapse">
                            <h3>Data security</h3>
                            <div class="text">Educational institutions hold data on staff, students and other
                                stakeholders. Much of this data is at risk and is an attractive target for bad actors.
                            </div>
